msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gu1iBdF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgu1iBdF.png&h=b6cf4831&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11f61901382862009df444cd57206cd4375cbe6d","tid":2046020,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:18:08.000Z","msg":"冇反對都唔會去<br />\n要悼念自己屋企點支蠟燭都得"},{"pid":"f2ea0817a6ec6b4c4d529fb4a6a61d60d5b41d11","tid":2046020,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗 全方面打壓港人"},{"pid":"80532d77de86fad3319b01378ea7906d90749f91","tid":2046020,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方就今年六四維園燭光集會，向支聯會發出反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方引用法例第599G章，禁止多於八人群組在公眾地方聚集的措施，有效至六月四日為理由，反對支聯會舉辦今年的六四維園燭光集會。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，有理由相信舉辦集會不僅會增加參與者感染新冠病毒的風險，亦會令所有市民的健康構成重大威脅，危害他人的權利。<br />\n<br />\n警方指相信對集會施加條件，亦無助阻止影響公共安全，所以反對集會舉行。"},{"pid":"5b051382b32dd8f8a32767f87089e63ab89c4757","tid":2046020,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f29b17a89be0b7534990fcb90e98b9b1539fd4","tid":2046020,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gu1iBdF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgu1iBdF.png&h=b6cf4831&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:28:16.000Z","msg":"6/4咁岩國歌法表決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c53aa99e023de59891a884bcb9b4a30f02debf","tid":2046020,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"ＷＦＣ"},{"pid":"a97a100fa70853f9e0b1f08d609db8f50fc81150","tid":2046020,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"敵反我擁"},{"pid":"ad7442559125f22b425dddbb434c8ae9cbc4bc47","tid":2046020,"uid":244346,"li